In [8]:
def feat_vec_repr(fv: np.array) -> str:
    components = []
    for i in range(fv.shape[0]):
        if fv[i] > 0:
            components.append(f'{vocab[i]} * {fv[i]}')
    return ' + '.join(components)

$$\text{Cosine Simliarity of }\mathbf A\text{ and }\mathbf B={\mathbf A\cdot\mathbf B\over \left\lVert \mathbf A \right\rVert \left\lVert \mathbf B \right\rVert}$$
In [12]:
def cosine_similarity(fv1: np.array, fv2: np.array) -> float:
    assert(fv1.shape[0] == fv2.shape[0])
    return fv1.dot(fv2) / (np.linalg.norm(fv1) * np.linalg.norm(fv2))

In [16]:
def unit_vec(vec: list[float]) -> list[float]:
    sq_sum = sum(map(lambda x: x ** 2, vec))
    norm = sq_sum ** .5
    assert(norm != 0)
    return list(map(lambda x: x / norm, vec))
